  "text": "SOC can therefore be considered as a psychosocial factor capable of exerting an effect on how health is perceived. It has also been shown to be a predictor for establishing healthy behaviors and positive self-perceptions of oral health [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] . However, SOC has not been investigated in adolescents in relation to self-perception of malocclusion.",
